# PATCH: 0029-template-script-editor
# WHY: User (SMB IT) chua co script trong repo -> can tao/sua file .yml/.sh/.ps1 ngay tren UI
#      va commit vao git local, khong phai clone repo + dung git ngoai.
# WHAT: Template form them nut "New/Edit file" o o script filename -> mo editor (codemirror),
#       dien sample theo app type; Luu -> POST /gitea/file -> commit vao repo local (Gitea).
#       Backend hook mong; logic Gitea Contents API o giteamanager ngoai cay upstream.
# SPEC: docs/L2-specs/core-patches/0029-template-script-editor.md
# BASELINE: v2.18.16
#
